race.comment: Several last start winners here. IMMINENT BOOM (3) is one of those who was having his second start for the new yard and led throughout to score. Going well and will give a huge sight over the longer journey. BAILE FERVOR (1) finished a 3.5 lengths third on dirt at Birdsville two back then followed up with another minor placing on turf at Emerald over 1200m. Overdue for a win and should prove hard to hold out. EXTREMELY FRILLY (6) is a veteran mare way better than last start. Previous for sound and gets a chance to atone. RED SUTURE (5) improved sharply on his fourth two starts back at this track with success over 1200m at Winton. Should run well again. MAKEMINEMILO (2) is another going well and hard to beat again.
